{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"28ba1af3db","title":"浙江省高级人民法院赔偿委员会来信答复通知书","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"ebbeb85a5f","index":0,"year":2006,"month":5,"day":23,"articleId":"28ba1af3db"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"cf6066d2fa","name":"浙江文革","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"30074f3f86","type":"title","text":"浙江省高级人民法院赔偿委员会来信答复通知书","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"28ba1af3db"},{"id":"88b34c5cdb","type":"appellation","text":"叶天和：","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"28ba1af3db"},{"id":"87e50baf48","type":"paragraph","text":"你（单位）来信收悉，现答复如下：根据你来信内容，你被判处徒刑和执行刑罚的时间均发生在国家赔偿法施行的1994年12月31日以前，依照最高人民法院法复（1995）1号批复，应依照以前的有关规定处理，因此，你的情况不适用国家赔偿法规定的赔偿范围，你应按相关落实政策的规定去处理。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"28ba1af3db"},{"id":"d3fe679ea4","type":"paragraph","text":"特此通知","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"28ba1af3db"},{"id":"6e76cf9476","type":"appellation","text":"浙江省高级人民法院信访专用章","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"28ba1af3db"},{"id":"2e420a0249","type":"appellation","text":"2006年5月23日","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"28ba1af3db"},{"id":"e3d4d6ffb4","type":"appellation","text":"杭州萧山区人民法院信访室对右派叶天和《索赔书》的回应","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"28ba1af3db"},{"id":"6b369f120f","type":"appellation","text":"2007.11.28","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"28ba1af3db"},{"id":"4c12e92bbb","type":"appellation","text":"叶天和：","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"28ba1af3db"},{"id":"e8019a8586","type":"paragraph","text":"你给最高人民法院的《索赔书》已转来我院。你1960年被本院以反革命罪判处有期徒刑8年。1979年纠正。你要求按国家赔偿法赔偿59年至79年因冤假错案的损失865959元。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"28ba1af3db"},{"id":"c21b7bbba5","type":"paragraph","text":"《国家赔偿法》是1995年1月1日起实施的，不溯及既往。而你的问题发生在国家赔偿法实施前，因此不适用国家赔偿法。你来信后，我们也走访了你原来的单位杭州闸口艮山门电厂留守管理处，他们认为，你79年纠错后，原杭州闸口电厂已让你回原单位落实了工作，工资和一切福利待遇与其他职工都是一样的，政治上经济上均没有歧视，退休等待遇均一视同仁。根据当时情况，该办的已经办理。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"28ba1af3db"},{"id":"f9cffa8b5d","type":"appellation","text":"杭州萧山区人民法院信访室","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"28ba1af3db"},{"id":"676363831d","type":"appellation","text":"2007年11月28日","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"28ba1af3db"}],"page":{"id":"42e12eafd4","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"28ba1af3db","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}